{"tid":761320,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★[突發]冇炒家推冧個市 都係炒樓最穩陣","createTime":"2018-07-30T09:43:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-30T11:35:55.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"963afac8108881a8b646c1630ec62aecf11f481a","tid":761320,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T09:43:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/_QUPb.b912idR0C2h8QLnQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9OTQwO2g9NDky/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/centralmarket.tumblr.com/9b2a8c987dc217f1d43578cf7b3369a5\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F_QUPb.b912idR0C2h8QLnQ--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9OTQwO2g9NDky%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Fcentralmarket.tumblr.com%2F9b2a8c987dc217f1d43578cf7b3369a5&h=93822825&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n話說今日有細價股投資者，見報呻冤話俾國際金融大鱷「360HK」呃錢，呃佢要不斷補倉。但散戶睇完單新聞後，好明顯唔多同情，仲話呢啲手法，其實只係以前班炒家用來焗散戶上船嘅老土招，只係大有大食、細有細食。<br />\n<br />\n開離岸空殼公司做「貸款人」、假網站、一出事就辦公室人去樓空等等，係唔係新招，認真見仁見智，大家自己識睇，筆者反而想引述其中一位散戶回應，佢話股市凶險，都係樓市安全，仲話：「都係買磚頭安全啲，冇炒家推冧個市」。<br />\n<br />\n原文如下：<br />\n<br />\n「83年用27萬5購入第一個連車位單位，現時升值40倍，98年用8萬多元買租置，現在&hellip;&hellip;嘻嘻！<br />\n<br />\n06年用128萬購入第三個單位，現在升值7倍，哈哈！」<br />\n<br />\n近年朋友之間，流行講一個叫心臟病指數，就係搵錢以外，個投資項目，會唔會令你心臟有事。睇返近年樓市走勢，無論係CCL抑或CCI，依該位散戶思路，的確係「買磚頭安全啲」，今時今日炒樓，無咁易有心臟病，尤其係一把年紀，身體唔好，人自然慢慢迷信「磚頭」，講起來都有啲生理原因。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>近年又的確係少咗人講「我要等03年再現時入市」嘅觀點，眼下多數係業主持貨自住或仔女住，如果真係有炒家想「推冧個市」，估計結果都只係兩敗俱傷，你覺得，炒家會唔會咁做？<br />\n反而，炒股真係炒到心臟病，尤其見到中伏股、清盤股，同埋騰訊兩嘢就穿，個心真係離一離。<br />\n筆者朋友結論係：「炒樓唔使煩。」唔知你又同唔同意呢？</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/%E7%86%B1%E8%A9%B1-%E5%86%87%E7%82%92%E5%AE%B6%E6%8E%A8%E5%86%A7%E5%80%8B%E5%B8%82-%E9%83%BD%E4%BF%82%E7%82%92%E6%A8%93%E6%9C%80%E7%A9%A9%E9%99%A3-032233054.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%25E7%2586%25B1%25E8%25A9%25B1-%25E5%2586%2587%25E7%2582%2592%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E6%258E%25A8%25E5%2586%25A7%25E5%2580%258B%25E5%25B8%2582-%25E9%2583%25BD%25E4%25BF%2582%25E7%2582%2592%25E6%25A8%2593%25E6%259C%2580%25E7%25A9%25A9%25E9%2599%25A3-032233054.html&d=FN1IPIf6A5MM2oCOz3Xkk26tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=41fe7e6d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/%E7%86%B1%E8%A9%B1-%E5%86%87%E7%82%92%E5%AE%B6%E6%8E%A8%E5%86%A7%E5%80%8B%E5%B8%82-%E9%83%BD%E4%BF%82%E7%82%92%E6%A8%93%E6%9C%80%E7%A9%A9%E9%99%A3-032233054.html</a>"},{"pid":"48f8020bf42368779c127c3e33ef13b67741fb2e","tid":761320,"uid":42921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T09:44:56.000Z","msg":"岩丫岩丫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6713e239b0b2233590773b6074b1cdca8148105b","tid":761320,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T09:45:19.000Z","msg":"尤其見到中伏股、清盤股，同埋<span style=\"color: red;\">騰訊兩嘢就穿</span>，個心真係離一離。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nall in 700<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ccbf266745a576ee4f7de5e423fc26427296b6a","tid":761320,"uid":13663,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T09:49:06.000Z","msg":"岩牙岩牙"},{"pid":"b3297502265131094b21930305c7ff1a71b39a4c","tid":761320,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T09:51:45.000Z","msg":"中8000萬六合彩，一定全部買晒樓，十年後身家至少8億"},{"pid":"54f25cf2fd82e767b7dcedcb18f2a6a233776300","tid":761320,"uid":24660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6713e239b0b2233590773b6074b1cdca8148105b","tid":761320,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T09:45:19.000Z","msg":"尤其見到中伏股、清盤股，同埋<span style=\"color: red;\">騰訊兩嘢就穿</span>，個心真係離一離。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nall in 700<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T09:52:43.000Z","msg":"點睇樓市"},{"pid":"9ebb51224f59cec856353bf423c0a9b75ef64613","tid":761320,"uid":26752,"l